title: Lazarus and the Power of Death
itunes:title: Lazarus and the Power of Death
description: Death is not a condition God desires for us . Rather, God wants us to have life. However, death is a reality; but it is not the final word. Christ is the final Word - namely, the life-giving Word. Christ brings Lazarus back to life. He desires to do the same for us.
